<+><html>\r\n<head>\r\n<title>stories.TC_006_UOP</title>\r\n<style type=\"text/css\" media=\"all\">\r\n@import url( \"./style/jbehave-core.css\" );\r\n</style>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<div class=\"story\">\r\n<h1>&#65279;</h1>\r\n<div class=\"path\">stories/TC_006_UOP.story</div>\r\n<div class=\"scenario\">\r\n<h2>Scenario: TC_001_UOP UOP  Create Internal Correspondence</h2>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">Given  I navigate to 'http://172.16.30.82:8888/login.aspx'</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">And  I login as 'alaa.abdelbagi' with password 'Aa1'</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">And  I click on 'Add Process Button'</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">And  I click on 'Internal Correspondence Button'</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">When  Set 'Subject Field' value to 'random'</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">And  I select '2 | &#1608;&#1581;&#1583;&#1577; &#1575;&#1604;&#1585;&#1602;&#1575;&#1576;&#1577;' from the 'Internal Correspondence Commissioner Destination' combo box</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">And  I click on 'Save Draft Button'</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">And  I click on 'Save Button'</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">And  I wait for '3' sec</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">And  I get value from 'Internal Correspondence Commissioner Destination' and save it as 'ComboBoxValue'</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">And  I get text from 'Subject Field' and save it as 'SubjectText'</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">And  I get value from 'Internal Correspondence Get Serial Number' and save it as 'InternalCorrespondenceSerialNumberValue'</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">And  I click on 'Direction Button'</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">And  I select '2 | &#1608;&#1581;&#1583;&#1577; &#1575;&#1604;&#1585;&#1602;&#1575;&#1576;&#1577;' from the 'Division Input' combo box</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">And  I wait for '3' sec</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">